title: adidas Skateboarding Sieben & Friends
description:
Michael Sieben teams up with adidas to create an imaginative quest with his furry monster friends based off of a treasure map they found while skating a ditch.  Official Website: http://www.adidas.com/skateboarding 
Store Locator: http://bit.ly/qIFMfO
